<p>Have you connected your current LED’s to “last year’s” robot, to verify that the LEDs are compatible with your original code.  (motto: Assume Nothing)</p>
<p>Also, I wondered if perhaps you had a RoboRio1 last year, but are using RoboRio 2’s this year.  I don’t know if there should be any difference, but it’s possible that this may effect the LED timing.</p>
<p>Phil.</p>","post_number":5,"post_type":1,"posts_count":6,"updated_at":"2024-04-02T14:40:00.787Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":null,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":59,"readers_count":58,"score":11.8,"yours":false,"topic_id":460852,"topic_slug":"addressable-leds-questions","display_username":"PhilBot","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":true,"can_wiki":false,"read":true,"user_title":"","bookmarked":false,"actions_summary":[],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":5633,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":true,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/addressable-leds-questions/460852/5","custom_user_title":null,"reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null},{"id":3577889,"name":"system","username":"system","avatar_template":"/uploads/default/original/4X/9/3/2/93234578e69f55873c63fc00fe2d0d85f23bce55.png","created_at":"2025-04-02T14:40:06.187Z","cooked":"<p>This topic was automatically closed 365 days after the last reply. New replies are no longer allowed.</p>","post_number":6,"post_type":3,"posts_count":6,"updated_at":"2025-04-02T14:40:06.187Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":null,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":2,"reads":1,"readers_count":0,"score":10.2,"yours":false,"topic_id":460852,"topic_slug":"addressable-leds-questions","display_username":"system","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":tru